Name: How, with tools?
Subhead: Calibre
Notes: When converting: best results are from HTML to EPUB. Converting from word processor docs may result in messy CSS.

GUI-driven, cross platform e-book manager

* http://calibre-ebook.com/
* drivers for tons of devices 
* lots of converters
* content server
* nice e-reader
* command-line tools for batch conversions

<pre>
<code>
ebook-convert input_file output_file [options]
</code>
</pre>